><strong><span style="color: #000066;"><span style="color: #000066; font-weight: bold;"> </span></span></strong><strong><span style="color: #000099;"><span style="color: #000099; font-weight: bold;"><br /> <br /> " Today, </span></span></strong><br /> <strong><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; color: #000099; font-size: x-small;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000099; font-weight: bold;"> ''</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; color: #000099; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; color: #000099; font-weight: bold;">I love you'' no   longer means </span></span></strong><br /> <strong><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; color: #000099; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; color: #000099; font-weight: bold;"> you are the only   one I love</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; color: #000099; font-size: x-small;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000099; font-weight: bold;">. </span></span></strong><br /> <strong><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; color: #000099; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; color: #000099; font-weight: bold;"> It is only an   expression of feeling,"</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: x-small;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-weight: bold;"> </span></span></strong><br /> <strong><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; color: #000099;"><span style="color: #000099; font-weight: bold;"> says psychiatrist</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; color: #000066;"><span style="color: #000066; font-weight: bold;"><br /> </span></span></strong><span style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="https://mail.google.com/mail/?ui=2&amp;ik=298564e48b&amp;view=att&amp;th=113d95b154a80670&amp;attid=0.2&amp;disp=emb&amp;realattid=0.2&amp;zw" border="0" alt="gurlzgroup  [www.friendmails.net.tc]" width="345" height="493" /></span><strong><span style="font-fa